A few notes on the CryoFeast coming Sunday, Dec 15th at the Creekside Preserve Lodge in Mayer, Arizona.

1.    We now have several people who are bringing deserts.  We can use something in the other fields below;
    Salads,  cold veggies
    Bread - rolls, bagels, 
    Side dishes (potatoes, beans, hot veggies) 
    Beverages (pop, juice)
    
2.    Drop me a line ( pizer@cox.net ) and let me know what you are bringing, so I can coordinate.

